---
title: Honey-Garlic Salmon with Ginger-Soy Veggies and Garlic Rice
description: Tender salmon with a sweet honey-garlic drizzle, what could be better? Pair that with buttery garlic rice and aromatic stir-fried carrots and bok choy, and you've got a speedy, simple and satisfying meal! No need to fuss over this one!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/saumon-au-miel-et-a-lail-778f2042.jpg
